titles.title: A bill to extend the temporary suspension of duty on 0,0-dimethyl-S{(4-oxo-1,2,3-benzotriazin-3-(4H)-yl)methyl} phosphorodithioate.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S5945)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 5/13/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1995, the duty on O,O-Dimethyl-S-(4-oxo-1,2,3-benzotriazin-3-(4H)-yl) methyl) phosphorodithioate.
